  				ois.readBoolean(),
  				ois.readBoolean(),
  				null
  		);
  	}
  
  	@Override
  	public PersistenceContext getPersistenceContext() {
  		throw new AssertionFailure( "Session/PersistenceContext is not available from an ImmutableEntityEntry" );
